00:37:52,920 --> 00:38:13,680
 Holy Spirit, I thank you.

774
00:38:13,680 --> 00:38:17,240
 You always come and pour out God's love into our hearts,

775
00:38:17,240 --> 00:38:22,240
 come and heal our wounds, come and embrace us,

776
00:38:22,240 --> 00:38:26,240
 come and draw near to us so that we could feel secure,

777
00:38:26,240 --> 00:38:27,240
 we could feel loved.

778
00:38:27,240 --> 00:38:28,560
 I thank you for that.

