00:38:38,840 --> 00:38:42,040
 and you would transform our character

783
00:38:42,040 --> 00:38:44,560
 so that we look more like Jesus.

784
00:38:44,560 --> 00:38:47,760
 And that's what I'm praying for right now, Holy Spirit.

