00:38:47,760 --> 00:38:50,480
 Come, come and fill us.

786
00:38:50,480 --> 00:38:57,000
 Come and fill the body of Jesus in this room right now.

787
00:38:57,000 --> 00:39:07,560
 God, I don't pray that we, by our effort,

788
00:39:07,560 --> 00:39:10,000
 we would close that gap between our reputation

789
00:39:10,000 --> 00:39:13,120
 and what our faith actually stands for.

790
00:39:13,120 --> 00:39:15,400
 But I do pray that we can close that gap

791
00:39:15,400 --> 00:39:21,480
 between your word and the reality

792
00:39:21,480 --> 00:39:24,520
 of our heart and our character right now.

793
00:39:24,520 --> 00:39:27,600
 I pray that you would come and close that gap,

794
00:39:27,600 --> 00:39:29,120
 that you would come and grow us.

795
00:39:29,120 --> 00:39:32,400
 We pray that we would be a community

796
00:39:32,400 --> 00:39:35,680
 that really grow big people,

797
00:39:35,680 --> 00:39:39,520
 people who demonstrate the character of Jesus,

798
00:39:39,520 --> 00:39:43,960
 who shows the mercy, who shows the love,

799
00:39:43,960 --> 00:39:47,560
 who shows the servant heart of Jesus in our city.

800
00:39:47,560 --> 00:39:53,000
 I pray that if there are strongholds in our hearts,

801
00:39:53,000 --> 00:39:55,520
 if there are things that are hindering us

802
00:39:55,520 --> 00:39:57,000
 from moving in that direction,

803
00:39:57,000 --> 00:40:00,440
 I pray that by the power of resurrection right now,

804
00:40:00,440 --> 00:40:04,360
 you would come and destroy those strongholds in our life

805
00:40:04,360 --> 00:40:08,400
 and you will take every thought of us captive right now.

806
00:40:09,280 --> 00:40:12,080
 I pray that we could align our hearts

807
00:40:12,080 --> 00:40:15,480
 with yours today once again, Lord.

808
00:40:15,480 --> 00:40:18,760
 Come and fill us.

809
00:40:18,760 --> 00:40:21,760
 Come and fill us up, Lord.

810
00:40:21,760 --> 00:40:25,720
 We need your grace.

811
00:40:25,720 --> 00:40:27,120
 We need your mercy.

812
00:40:27,120 --> 00:40:29,600
 We need your encouragement.

813
00:40:29,600 --> 00:40:34,200
 We need you to come and be that fire inside of us.

814
00:40:34,200 --> 00:40:37,440
 Keep burning inside of us.

815
00:40:38,440 --> 00:40:41,560
 Until our hearts fully burn for Jesus

816
00:40:41,560 --> 00:40:43,240
 and we only live for him.

817
00:40:43,240 --> 00:40:46,120
 So come, Lord.

818
00:40:46,520 --> 00:40:47,680
 So come, Lord.

